race.comment: COOL FIZZ (1) working herself into form and near her top now third-up. Sat on the fast tempo when a narrow second over 1005m at Taree. Placed at this track and senior rider hops on. YES YES BOSS (8) showed good early speed before folding up in the straight when fourth over 1000m at Wellington. Will push forward again and assess on earlier runs. Each way. NIKODY'S DIEGO (9) surprised at the big odds when up in trip for a game on-pace second over 1258m at Taree. Well placed from the gate and expected to take a hand in the finish. INVINCIBLE WHIP (3) capable on his day and the tongue-tie comes off for this. Goes well at the trip and arrives here in peak condition.
